    <text>
    <body>
        
        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>33 Raphael Street | Brompton S.W. | (London)</placeName>
                    <date>31/3/78.</date>
                    <salute>Sir,</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>It may seem rather an unscientific question to ask, but I have often wondered why it is that pigeons always fly in a circle. If you would be so good as to inform me their reason for so-doing I should feel deeply obliged.</p>
<p>I remain, Sir, | Yr very ob<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>. sert— | J. W. Howell <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/></p>
<p rend="left">Chas. Darwin Esq M.A. F.R.S. LL.D</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div> 
         
        
        
            
            <div type="footnotes">
                <note xml:id="foot.f1">The correspondent has not been identified.</note>       
        </div>
    
